reviewText: This movie is great, not a classic but a very scary movie (if paranormal films frighten you). Horror doesn't usually scare me but paranormal films usually keep me on the edge of my seat. I must recommend.
I hate it.  Mostly because the disc did not work in my DVD player.
Excellent movie, interesting point of view. Michael does a great job.  Fast delivery.

My wife and I really love this movie.  We had it on dvd, but wanted to see what it was like in blu-ray.  I really can't say that I can tell that much difference, but still love the movie.  It is very entertaining and thought Keaton was very good.  I would say that you would like to watch the science fiction, thriller types of movies to like it though.  Just an FYI, that there are 2 of these movies.  This one and a sequel.
Come on Michael you're better than this
